en bad for the companies=E2=80=99 stock prices, for what I hope are obvious=
 discounted-cash-flow-related reasons.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I do=
 not have any special insight into=C2=A0<em>why=C2=A0</em>Chinese regulator=
