me,=E2=80=9D she says. =E2=80=9CSometimes, I wake up in the middle of the n=
ight and I think, =E2=80=98I stole that. I stole his voice.=E2=80=99 You kn=
ow that=E2=80=99s like stealing somebody=E2=80=99s soul, right? That tape i=
s not mine to give or sell.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Not lo=
ng after our conversation, Eppes called me to let me know she=E2=80=99d upd=
ated her will. The tape now will be placed, along with her body, in the cre=
matorium.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Burning a unique cul=
tural artifact? You know what that means! It=E2=80=99s the =E2=80=9C<a href=
